    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this beauty\u2014it\u2019s an absolute dream! It\u2019s been kept in such incredible shape that it basically looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot. From the spotless interior to the flawless finish, you can really tell it\u2019s been truly loved and pampered. It runs like a charm and is totally ready for its next adventure. You've gotta see it in person\u2014I promise you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
