    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that defies its age. This car has been pampered in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in a finish that retains its original showroom luster without a single swirl mark or stone chip. The interior is a masterclass in preservation; the premium leather remains supple and free of creases, still carrying that distinct 'new car' aroma. Every button, switch, and electronic feature operates with tactile precision, exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive folder of preventative maintenance records performed exclusively by certified technicians. This is not just a used car; it is a meticulously curated piece of automotive excellence for the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
