    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly spectacular, showroom-ready shape\u2014it\u2019s been pampered in a garage and looks practically brand new inside and out. No scratches, no spills, just pure driving bliss! It\u2019s been my baby, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it just as much as I have. You seriously won't find another one this clean\u2014come take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
