    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example of the S54 platform. The high-revving 3.2L straight-six features an 8,000 RPM redline and instantaneous throttle response via its individual throttle bodies. Mated to a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a mechanical variable M-differential lock, the drivetrain provides a pure, analog connection to the road. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive Vanos overhaul and rod bearing replacement. The chassis is pristine with no subframe fatigue, and the suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics. This is a turn-key collector piece with zero mechanical compromise.",
